p401
aVIt's not a sin."
p402
aVBut as I left that night, I was certain that somehow
p403
aVI'd traded the life of my everlasting soul
p404
aVfor this one night with Roy Campanella.
p405
aV(Laughter)
p406
aVAnd there were no indulgences around that I could buy.
