aVSo I had this sin on my soul when I went to my first confession.
p408
aVI told the priest right away.
p409
aVHe said, "No problem. It wasn't a religious service."
p410
aVBut then, unfortunately, he said, "And what else, my child?"
p411
aa(lp412
VAnd then came my second sin.
p413
aVI tried to sandwich it in between talking too much in church,
p414
aVwishing harm to others, being mean to my sisters.
